  <bioghist id="aspace_2165aaf049f319390d41959d6f78579a">
    <head>Historical/Biographical Note</head>
<p>The Red Falcons of America was a socialist organization for children between the ages of 8 and 15, established ca. 1932, and affiliated with the Socialist Party (U.S.).</p>  </bioghist>
